These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose, balloon-flower, dahlia
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, family, superhero, western
4 different games are played: whist, scrabble, canasta, bridge
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, december, october
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, mango, apricot, pineapple
 1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating mango##1
 4. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the person watching western movies is the person watching western movies##1
 6. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
10. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
11. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
12. the person playing canasta is between the person watching superhero movies and the person playing scrabble##2
13. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person eating pineapple##1
14. the person eating apricot is the person who growsrose##1
15. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Flower           | daffodil | balloon-flower | dahlia  | rose    |
| Movie-Genre   | family     | western   | superhero  | adventure  |
| Game           | scrabble        | canasta    | bridge        | whist |
| Birthday         | october    | january      | september   | december    |
| Food     | grapefruit  | pineapple     | mango | apricot |

