.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, pony, mouse, chinchilla
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bluemaster, prince, bongani
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, martial-arts, thriller
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy, lily, orchid
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, scientist, designer, manager
 1. the engineer is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the designer##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is the scientist##1
 6. the prince-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is in an even position##4
 8. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
 9. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
10. the game-smoker is the manager##1
11. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
12. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
13. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Pet      | mouse        | chinchilla       | frog    | pony       |
| Cigar         | prince | bluemaster      | bongani | game |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller     | martial-arts | comedy  | animation   |
| Flower   | daisy   | orchid         | amaryllis   | lily      |
| Job         | scientist      | engineer     | designer    | manager      |

