.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, disaster, zombie, western
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, pakistani, french, colombian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, house, indie, jazz
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, backgammon, canasta
House: futuristic, art-deco, townhouse, ranch-style
 1. the person playing billiard is the fan of house##1
 2. the fan of house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 3. the ranch-style house is in an odd position##4
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the australian##3
 5. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
 6. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
 7. the colombian is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 8. the futuristic house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 9. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
10. the person watching zombie movies is the fan of indie##1
11. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
12. the fan of jazz is on the right of the french##1
13. the person playing backgammon is the person watching western movies##1
14. the fan of indie is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre          | zombie | disaster | satire     | western |
| Nationality           | french  | colombian   | australian | pakistani  |
