.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, superhero, zombie, thriller
4 different games are played: bridge, snooker, go, poker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, juice, water, milk
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, peas, banana, papaya
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, snowmobile, tram
 1. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 2. the person drinking water is the person watching zombie movies##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 4. the person drinking milk is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 5. the person eating cabbage is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 7. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
 8. the person eating peas is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
10. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
11. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
12. the person watching animation movies is the person playing poker##1
13. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
14. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
15. the person playing go is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |        4        |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller | superhero    | animation | zombie       |
| Game           | snooker | bridge  | poker   | go |
| Beverage   | tea   | juice     | milk      | water            |
| Food           | cabbage       | banana      | peas    | papaya           |
| Transport     | tram      | snowmobile | quad-bike   | jet-ski         |

