.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, emerald, ivory, turquise
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, librarian, nurse, security-guard
House: farmhouse, colonial, ranch-style, wooden
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, punk, reggae, folk
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, skateboard, scooter, quad-bike
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the scooter and the person who likes emerald##2
 2. the nurse is in an even position##4
 3. the colonial house is on the right of the nurse##1
 4. the security-guard is in an even position##4
 5. the fan of punk is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the fan of folk is on the right of the colonial house##1
 7. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
 9. the entrepreneur is the person who likes turquise##1
10. the person who likes emerald is the wooden house##1
11. the entrepreneur is the farmhouse house##1
12. the fan of reggae is the colonial house##1
13. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
14. the person who likes emerald is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |      3      |       4        |
| Color          | turquise   | fuchsia        | ivory      | emerald      |
| Job           | entrepreneur | nurse         | librarian   | security-guard |
| House   | farmhouse       | ranch-style          | colonial | wooden        |
| Music-Genre           | gospel         | punk    | reggae    | folk         |
| Transport         | skateboard     | scooter | quad-bike  | motorbike        |

