There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, azure, green, turquise
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is in an odd position##4
 3. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
 4. the person traveling to new-york is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who likes chestnut is the fan of classical##1
 6. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 7. the person who likes turquise is the fan of soul##1
 8. the person traveling to miami is the owner of the mouse##1
 9. the fan of punk is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating peach is the owner of the hamster##1
11. the person who likes turquise is in an odd position##4
12. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person who likes green##1
13. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
14. the person traveling to miami is between the person eating peach and the fan of punk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Pet      | frog    | hamster        | mouse      | snake   |
| Food          | raspberry   | peach      | grapefruit | blueberry  |
