 1. the person who growsmarigold is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who likes turquise is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is the pakistani##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who growsazalea##1
 5. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
 6. the person who growsmarigold is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who likes turquise##2
 7. the person who growsbellflower is between the canadian and the indian##2
 8. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 9. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the spanish##3
10. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
11. the person eating broccoli is the person who likes turquise##1
12. the indian is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

