 1. the person who likes brown is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person eating blueberry is the person playing bridge##1
 3. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4
 4. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 5. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is the person eating plum##1
 7. the person eating pear is in an even position##4
 8. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person driving the bike##3
 9. the person playing whist is the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
12. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing chess##1
13. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who likes white##1
14. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
