11. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
12. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
13. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
14. the person traveling to nizza is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | woodworking | skydiving  | filmmaking | singing  |
| Birthday   | september     | march    | may     | december      |
| Sport   | golf  | water-polo  | tennis     | ice-hockey |
| Cigar           | chaman      | davidoff | alhambra       | havana     |
| City     | miami      | san-francisco | nizza  | paris   |

